<h2 id="quick-note-about-tuning">Quick note about tuning!</h2>

<p>Nirvana plays with everything tuned down 1/2 step (E becomes Eb, A becomes Ab, etc). In my video lesson, Iâ€™m staying in standard tuning to keep things simple. There is an additional step (of tuning your low-E string down an extra whole step) which Iâ€™ll talk about later as well.</p>

